long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Fantasy Calendar is a Chrome Extension to add functionalities to fantasy yahoo baseball. With fantasy calendar you can schedule moves for a future date and automate your roster's start active players for every day.
Fantasy Calendar is a b2f3 tool (built by fans for fans). This extension will give you that last push to win your fantasy league. We hope you enjoy it.
